OL,3,CMinisters urged to act after police
OL,4,Cannounce front-desk closures at 11
OL,5,Cstations
OL,7,FThe Stormont justice and finance
OL,8,Fministers have been urged to act after
OL,9,Fthe police service announced plans to
OL,10,Fclose enquiry offices at 11 stations.
OL,12,FThe move, that will see four police
OL,13,Fstations in Belfast affected, as well
OL,14,Fas stations across the region, has
OL,15,Fbeen blamed on financial and resource
OL,16,Fpressures.
