OL,3,CMinisters urged to act after police
OL,4,Cannounce front-desk closures at 11
OL,5,Cstations
OL,7,FThe stations affected are Lisburn
OL,8,FRoad, Strand Town, Tennent Street and
OL,9,FWoodbourne in Belfast, as well as
OL,10,FBangor, Banbridge, Magherafelt,
OL,11,FDungannon, Lisnaskea, Waterside and
OL,12,FNewtownabbey.
OL,14,FThe inquiry office closures were
OL,15,Flikely to take place within three
OL,16,Fmonths, and were said to be designed
OL,17,Fto make a significant financial saving
OL,18,Fas well as maximise the availability
OL,19,Fof officers for critical service
OL,20,Fprovision within communities.
