OL,5,Cstations
OL,7,FAssistant Chief Constable Bobby
OL,8,FSingleton said the decision was taken
OL,9,Ffollowing an "extensive review, which
OL,10,Fincluded analysis of the volume and
OL,11,Ftype of demand in enquiry
OL,12,Foffices"."This review concluded that
OL,13,Fagainst the backdrop of wider resource
OL,14,Fchallenges, the current service is
OL,15,Fneither sustainable nor effective," he
OL,16,Fsaid.
