OL,7,FIndependent North Down MLA Alex Easton
OL,8,Fand UUP Fermanagh and South Tyrone MLA
OL,9,FTom Elliott raised concerns about the
OL,10,Fplan during a sitting of the Assembly
OL,11,Fon Tuesday.
OL,13,FMr Easton urged Justice Minister Naomi
OL,14,FLong to contact Finance Minister
OL,15,FCaoimhe Archibald, and raise the issue
OL,16,Fwith the Executive.
