OL,5,Cstations
OL,7,FHe said North Down was impacted by the
OL,8,Fclosure of Donaghadee police station
OL,9,Fin 2012 and the previous closure of
OL,10,Fthe enquiry office at Holywood police
OL,11,Fstation.Mr Easton described a "deeply
OL,12,Fworrying situation" and said he
OL,13,Fbelieved closing the enquiry offices
OL,14,Fwould be a "disaster for policing
OL,15,Fright across Northern Ireland"."
