OL,5,Cstations
OL,7,FAll of this is happening to save
OL,8,F#400,000. In the scheme of things,
OL,9,F#400,000 isn't a huge amount of money
OL,10,Fto keep all these enquiry offices open
OL,11,Fso I would implore the Justice
OL,12,FMinister to contact the Finance
OL,13,FMinister and to raise this issue at
OL,14,Fthe Northern Ireland Executive,
OL,15,Fbecause I believe this would be a
OL,16,Fdisaster for policing right across
OL,17,FNorthern Ireland," he told MLAs.
OL,19,FMr Elliott told MLAs the move was a
OL,20,F"huge blow of confidence in policing".
