OL,5,Cstations
OL,7,FHe said it left only one enquiry
OL,8,Foffice across the entire of Fermanagh
OL,9,Fand South Tyrone.He described the
OL,10,Fstation in Dungannon as "extremely
OL,11,Fbusy", while the Lisnaskea station
OL,12,F"serves a huge rural area around that
OL,13,Fsouth and east Fermanagh area"."
OL,15,FIt's going to be a considerable
OL,16,Fdistance for those people to travel
OL,17,Ffrom Roslea and the edges of
OL,18,FNewtownbutler and Derrylin to go to
OL,19,FEnniskillen enquiry office which is
OL,20,Fobviously not open all the time
OL,21,Feither," he said.
